data.description: MAKE US AN OFFER! Discover the epitome of modern living in this immaculate, fully remodeled 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home. Step into a world of elegance with stainless steel appliances, exquisite granite countertops, and a stylish island in the kitchen. Revel in the luxury of tiled kitchen and bathroom floors, complemented by pristine hardwood floors in the main living area. The finished basement offers a cozy family room with plush new carpeting, while a spacious back deck provides the perfect setting for outdoor enjoyment. This home leaves no detail untouched, boasting new windows, a resilient roof, sleek siding, updated plumbing and electrical systems, a new hot water tank, and a cutting-edge HVAC system. Elevate your lifestyle with this remarkable residence – an embodiment of sophistication and comfort.
